Ďakujem.

115
00:10:00,020 --> 00:10:01,020
Kai.

116
00:10:02,340 --> 00:10:04,020
Nezlom môjmu kamarátovi srdce.

117
00:10:12,380 --> 00:10:13,840
Veci, ktoré na Kai-ovi nenávidím.

118
00:10:13,840 --> 00:10:15,500
