163
00:12:45,020 --> 00:12:47,620
Po štvrté.
Kai je rodený hráč.

164
00:12:49,340 --> 00:12:51,600
Third, už idem!

165
00:12:55,420 --> 00:12:56,420
Milk.

166
00:12:57,380 --> 00:12:59,100
Prší.

167
00:12:59,340 --> 00:13:01,380
