178
00:13:21,400 --> 00:13:23,180
Takže to celé bolo iba divadlo.

179
00:13:23,180 --> 00:13:24,280
V skutočnosti ho chceš mať pre seba.

180
00:13:24,300 --> 00:13:25,400
Ty potkan!

181
